      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, making it an excellent candidate for a dependable daily driver. While the mechanical components are solid, you will find some minor cosmetic imperfections, such as small stone chips on the hood and slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. The interior is clean, non-smoking, and all electronics, including the infotainment and climate control, are fully functional. It has a complete service history and recently passed inspection, ensuring it's ready for the road with no immediate repairs needed.",
